Despana is the only food boutique in New York City specializing in foods from Spain.  Delicious sandwiches and tapas are prepared on site; wine and beer are served as well.  We also offer a pantry of olive oils, aged vinegars, pates, sweets, paprika, vegetables, anchovies, Iberico ham, chorizos, dry cured meats & over 50 specialty cheeses from all over Spain. 
